casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Edwin L. LONDON.
No. D-2880.
Supreme Court of the United States
Feb. 29, 2016.
Edwin L. London, of Langhorne, Pennsylvania, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
